series.title: Nobody Knows
series.core_mission: Teach AI through the radical honesty that even the creators are improvising, learning, and frequently surprised by their own creations
series.revolutionary_promise: We'll learn together by admitting what nobody wants to say out loud—that the most advanced technology in human history is built by people who are often as baffled by it as you are.
